to look after her?

05:31.243 --> 05:32.419
You can't miss my show.

05:32.462 --> 05:33.724
I already promised.

05:33.768 --> 05:36.248
And it's... such a big bunion.

05:38.686 --> 05:40.949
This is about Rob, isn't it?

05:40.992 --> 05:42.472
What?

05:42.516 --> 05:44.387
Just admit it.

05:44.431 --> 05:46.084
