of Rob and I's relationship.

05:52.482 --> 05:56.181
Believe me, that
is not the reason.

06:10.108 --> 06:12.284
I'm telling you,
we're lost.

06:12.328 --> 06:13.938
Well, maybe if you'd asked
for directions

06:13.982 --> 06:15.766
when we got off the highway...

06:15.810 --> 06:18.900
