you weren't successful.

07:23.268 --> 07:24.400
TOMMY: Uh,
she's with me, sir.

07:24.444 --> 07:25.793
She was just asking directions

07:25.836 --> 07:26.924
because we got lost.

07:26.968 --> 07:28.317
Relax, kid.
I'm doing you a favor.

07:28.360 --> 07:30.058
You don't want your first time
to be with a pro.

07:30.101 --> 07:31.276
How dare you?

07:31.320 --> 07:33.061
