Well, show him your license.

07:41.591 --> 07:42.897
My... Oh, uh...

07:42.940 --> 07:44.768
Uh...

07:46.553 --> 07:49.251
If we just met, how do I
know his name is Tommy Harte

07:49.294 --> 07:50.382
and that he lives in Pasadena

07:50.426 --> 07:52.602
