who is my best friend,

08:07.748 --> 08:10.228
and my husband, who is gay.

08:14.276 --> 08:17.279
Well, I got to give you points
for creativity.

08:18.280 --> 08:20.674
Have fun, kid.

08:30.031 --> 08:32.076
Eli! Hey, can you
walk Teacup for me?

08:32.120 --> 08:33.817
