been on the books for months.

08:39.823 --> 08:41.608
Honey, the people at your firm
know that we were attacked.

08:41.651 --> 08:44.045
I mean, they wouldn't blink
if you opted out.

08:44.088 --> 08:46.613
I know, but I told my sisters
I'm coming to town,

08:46.656 --> 08:48.658
and they're still threatening
to visit this summer,

08:48.702 --> 08:50.704
so we kind of want
to break the news

08:50.747 --> 08:52.967
