any more gas on that fire.

09:06.589 --> 09:10.027
You haven't met them yet,
but they're awful.

09:11.333 --> 09:12.595
All right, Teacup.

09:12.639 --> 09:14.075
Whoa, here we go.

09:14.118 --> 09:16.643
Yeah.

09:19.341 --> 09:20.821
Lamar.
Oh!

09:20.864 --> 09:22.562
