for weeks.

09:25.652 --> 09:27.305
No, no, no. No, I...

09:27.349 --> 09:29.525
I-I was absolutely
gonna call you back, man.

09:29.569 --> 09:31.527
I just...
I've been incredibly busy.

09:31.571 --> 09:33.573
I see you had time to get a dog.

09:33.616 --> 09:34.791
