09:34.835 --> 09:36.097
You'll like this.

09:36.140 --> 09:38.055
Finally had that threesome.

09:38.099 --> 09:40.623
I would ask what one has to do
with the other,

09:40.667 --> 09:41.929
but never the fuck mind.

09:41.972 --> 09:44.322
Where is my script?Script?

09:44.366 --> 09:46.586
The one you promised
would be done a month ago?

09:46.629 --> 09:48.239
The one I talked up
to Paramount.

09:48.283 --> 09:50.067
Got 'em all excited,
and now they're pissed off

09:50.111 --> 09:51.591
wondering what happened to it.

09:51.634 --> 09:52.940
Well, it-it's almost done.

09:52.983 --> 09:55.290
I'm just... making
a few final tweaks.

09:55.333 --> 09:56.900
Oh, please.

09:56.944 --> 09:59.424
The only line older than that
is "let there be light."

09:59.468 --> 10:01.557
No, I'm not lying.
Look, I-I swear to you--

10:01.601 --> 10:03.472
I swear to you, I will have it
to you in one week.

10:03.515 --> 10:06.083
No. You got 24 hours.

10:06.127 --> 10:08.477
Starting now.

10:08.520 --> 10:10.653
Come on, man, we're
supposed to be friends.

10:10.697 --> 10:12.350
Look, I am your friend.
Any other agent would have

10:12.394 --> 10:14.048
kicked your ass
to the curb long ago.

10:14.091 --> 10:15.223
Okay, well, yeah, and of course,

10:15.266 --> 10:16.659
I'm grateful
that you stood by me,

10:16.703 --> 10:18.705
but please, I mean--
Give me till Friday.

10:18.748 --> 10:20.663
