and water their plants

11:51.319 --> 11:52.276
while they're at work

11:52.320 --> 11:53.800
or on vacation.

11:53.843 --> 11:55.018
Will he?

11:55.062 --> 11:56.628
This is where
the favor comes in.

11:56.672 --> 11:59.370
I'm asking all of my friends
to hire Tommy.

11:59.414 --> 12:01.329
I need to keep him busy.

12:01.372 --> 12:04.071
Just so I'm clear,
people leave town

12:04.114 --> 12:05.768
