12:13.602 --> 12:16.431
I'm sure he'd stay long enough
to get the job done.

12:16.474 --> 12:18.476
Of course.

12:18.520 --> 12:20.565
Can I count you in?

12:20.609 --> 12:21.741
Oh, why not?

12:21.784 --> 12:23.003
We like Tommy,
don't we, darling?

12:23.046 --> 12:24.613
Oh, yes.

12:24.656 --> 12:27.050
We certainly do.

12:27.094 --> 12:28.269
BETH ANN:
Poor April.

12:28.312 --> 12:30.053
