13:31.985 --> 13:33.029
And these are for Tuesday?

13:33.073 --> 13:35.031
Yeah.

13:35.075 --> 13:36.380
ROB:
What's wrong?

13:36.424 --> 13:39.079
Well, I just want to make sure

13:39.122 --> 13:41.603
we haven't forgotten
about any plans

13:41.646 --> 13:44.214
