13:44.258 --> 13:46.826
Well, whatever plans we made,
consider them canceled.

13:46.869 --> 13:50.090
I've got a date with my wife,
the Dodgers and the Yankees.

13:50.133 --> 13:52.092
Okay.

13:52.135 --> 13:54.137
