to you being so wonderful.

14:00.230 --> 14:01.623
Oh.

14:01.666 --> 14:03.190
Huh?

14:03.233 --> 14:05.757
Rob, give us a second. We're not
through with the mopping.

14:07.063 --> 14:09.326
I got to call Carl.

14:09.370 --> 14:11.981
